data.description: Beautiful home on corner fenced lot with large bedrooms. New HVAC system, New Hot water Heater, New Dishwasher. 4-year-old roof. Large living room with bay window and wood burning fireplace. Spacious kitchen with room for barstools at counter. Oversized Breakfast eating area. Primary bedroom with private ensuite. Laundry in the Full Bath on the main floor. Laminate flooring in living room. Kitchen and Dining room flooring is tile. Prewired for an attic fan. Full basement just waiting to make your own. Oversized garage, with great storage and epoxy floors for easy maintenance. Invisible fence in yard.
